text: The Parliament of Nauru is the unicameral legislature of Nauru. It has 19 members and they are elected for a three-year term in multi-seat constituencies. The President of Nauru is elected by the members of the Parliament."About Parliament", Parliament of Nauru The number of seats was increased to 19 in 2013."Nauru country brief" , Australian Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade.
